Simple install procedure
========================

  % gzip -cd adns_tsar-2.1.0.tar.gz | tar xvf -  # unpack the sources
  % cd adns_tsar-2.1.0                           # change to the toplevel directory
  % make                                    # build adns_tsar

  [ Become root if necessary ]
  % make install                            # install adns_tsar
  % make uninstall                          # uninstall adns_tsar
  [ if you want install adns_tsardevel ]
  % make adns_tsardevel
  % make uninstall

RPM install
========================

  %gzip -cd adns_tsar-2.1.0.tar.gz | tar xvf -  # unpack the sources
  %cd adns_tsar-2.1.0/rpm                       # change to the rpm directory
  %sh adns_tsar-build.sh .. adns_tsar 2.1.0 1        # create rpm for adns_tsar
  %rpm -ivh *.rpm                          # install adns_tsar by rpm

